221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text]The <strong>NSNP Entrepreneur Stream<\/strong> is designed for business owners or senior executives who desire to relocate to Nova Scotia. They must either start a new business or purchase an existing one, and they must be actively involved in the day-to-day management of the company.<\/p>\n<p>The entrepreneur may be nominated for permanent resident status after a year of operation. The feed is only open to those who have been invited. Programs like these play a crucial role in bolstering the economy by promoting more business practices and creating employment for residents in Nova Scotia.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; centered_text=&#8221;true&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][image_with_animation image_url=&#8221;9041&#8243; animation=&#8221;None&#8221; hover_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; alignment=&#8221;&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; box_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; image_loading=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; max_width_mobile=&#8221;default&#8221; img_link=&#8221;tel:+1(778)%638-0400&#8243;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row type=&#8221;full_width_content&#8221; full_screen_row_position=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; scene_position=&#8221;center&#8221; left_padding_desktop=&#8221;8%&#8221; right_padding_desktop=&#8221;8%&#8221; top_padding_phone=&#8221;10%&#8221; bottom_padding_phone=&#8221;15%&#8221; left_padding_phone=&#8221;7%&#8221; right_padding_phone=&#8221;7%&#8221; text_color=&#8221;dark&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; row_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; row_border_radius_applies=&#8221;bg&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; shape_divider_position=&#8221;bottom&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; shape_type=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; tablet_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; phone_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][nectar_highlighted_text color_type=&#8221;regular&#8221; highlight_color=&#8221;#ffc3b7&#8243; style=&#8221;half_text&#8221;]\n<h2><em>Eligibility Requirements<\/em><\/h2>\n[\/nectar_highlighted_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;bottom&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;30px&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text]Foreign entrepreneurs who wish to apply for immigration to Nova Scotia through the <strong>NSNP Entrepreneur Stream <\/strong>have to meet several qualifying requirements, including:[\/vc_column_text][toggles style=&#8221;default&#8221;][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Age&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650870134124{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]Applicants must be at least 21 years old to apply for the program.[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Net Worth&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650870448179{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]The individuals applying through this program must have a net worth of at least <strong>$600,000 CAD<\/strong>.[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Minimum Invest&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650870380921{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]Prospective entrepreneurs must be capable of investing at least <strong>$150,000 CAD<\/strong> or more to establish a business in Nova Scotia.[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Intent To Reside In The Province&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650810233600{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]The applicant must have the intention of permanently residing in Nova Scotia while owning and operating a business based in the province.[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Work Experience&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650870312437{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]All applicants must have at least <strong>three years of experience<\/strong> in owning and actively managing a business with one-third ownership, OR over five years of experience in a senior business management role.[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Language Proficiency&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650870244386{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]Applicants need to have a score of at least <strong>CLB 5<\/strong> in terms of speaking, writing, and comprehending the language. Additionally, applicants must have a score of at least 5 for reading and writing for English or French.[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Expression of Interest&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650870273528{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]Applicants must fill out and <a href=\"https:\/\/novascotia.ca\/sns\/access\/online-services\/immigration\/eoi-entrepreneur.asp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">submit an Expression of Interest<\/a> (EOI) to the Nova Scotia Office of Immigration (NSOI).[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][toggle color=&#8221;Default&#8221; title=&#8221;Nova Scotia Office of Immigration Invitation&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1650870292734{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;]Applicants must receive an <strong>Invitation To Apply<\/strong> from the NSOI after it reviews their EOI.[\/vc_column_text][\/toggle][\/toggles][image_with_animation animation=&#8221;Fade In&#8221; hover_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; alignment=&#8221;&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; box_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; image_loading=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; max_width_mobile=&#8221;default&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row type=&#8221;full_width_content&#8221; full_screen_row_position=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_color=&#8221;#f7f7f7&#8243; scene_position=&#8221;center&#8221; top_padding=&#822